<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Bilkha - The Land of Sagalsha</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; background: #fdf2e9; color: #4a235a; }
        .card { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: white; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background: #9b59b6; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .details { padding: 30px; }
        .landmark { color: #8e44ad; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="header"><h1>🏡 Bilkha Village</h1></div>
        <div class="details">
            <p><strong>District:</strong> Junagadh, Gujarat</p>
            <p><strong>History:</strong> Famous for the legend of <span class="landmark">Sheth Sagalsha</span>.</p>
            <p><strong>Top Landmark:</strong> Bilkheshwar Mahadev Temple</p>
            <p><strong>Proximity:</strong> Situated near the foothills of Mt. Girnar.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
